OL,3,CWelsh people awarded the King's
OL,4,Cbirthday honours
OL,6,FA prominent immunologist, Wales' chief
OL,7,Fscout volunteer, and a legendary 1958
OL,8,FWorld Cup footballer are among the
OL,9,Fpeople from Wales recognised in this
OL,10,Fyear's King's Birthday Honours list.
OL,12,FThe annual list celebrates the
OL,13,Foutstanding achievements and service
OL,14,Fof extraordinary people across the UK.
OL,16,FThis year's recipients from Wales
OL,17,Frepresent a range of fields, including
OL,18,Fpioneering medical research, frontline
OL,19,Fhealthcare, community, and rural
OL,20,Fagriculture.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/8
