OL,3,CWelsh people awarded the King's
OL,4,Cbirthday honours
OL,6,FA significant number of awards were
OL,7,Fgiven to professionals working at the
OL,8,Fforefront of the Welsh health and care
OL,9,Fsectors.
OL,11,FProfessor Stephen Jolles, a consultant
OL,12,Fimmunologist at the Immunodeficiency
OL,13,FCentre for Wales, based in Bont-Faen,
OL,14,FSouth Glamorgan, has been recognised
OL,15,Ffor his services to immunology and
OL,16,Frare diseases.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
