OL,3,CWelsh people awarded the King's
OL,4,Cbirthday honours
OL,6,FLeading the civic honours is Glynne
OL,7,FDavid Jones, lately the director of
OL,8,Fthe Wales Office, who has been
OL,9,Fappointed a CBE for his public service.
OL,11,FIn the philanthropic and environmental
OL,12,Fsectors, Professor Heather Vivienne
OL,13,FStevens CBE, from the Vale of
OL,14,FGlamorgan, was recognised for her
OL,15,Fextensive services to the environment,
OL,16,Fyoung people, and philanthropy in
OL,17,FWales.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/8
