OL,3,CWelsh people awarded the King's
OL,4,Cbirthday honours
OL,6,FProfessor Emeritus David Austin, based
OL,7,Fin Lampeter, Dyfed, was honoured for
OL,8,Fhis wide-ranging contributions to
OL,9,FWelsh heritage, economic regeneration,
OL,10,Fand his engagement with young people.
OL,12,FThe honours list also shines a light
OL,13,Fon individuals who have dedicated
OL,14,Ftheir lives to building stronger
OL,15,Fcommunities, preserving Welsh history,
OL,16,Fand protecting the environment.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/8
