OL,3,CWelsh people awarded the King's
OL,4,Cbirthday honours
OL,6,FA standout recognition goes to
OL,7,FProfessor Heather Vivienne Stevens CBE
OL,8,Fof the Vale of Glamorgan, whose award
OL,9,Fhighlights a lifetime of service to
OL,10,Fthe environment, her championing of
OL,11,Fyoung people, and her widespread
OL,12,Fphilanthropy across Wales.
OL,14,FSimilarly, Professor Emeritus David
OL,15,FAustin of Lampeter was recognised for
OL,16,Fhis immense contributions to the
OL,17,FHeritage of Wales, local economic
OL,18,Fregeneration, and his work inspiring
OL,19,Fyounger generations.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/8
