OL,3,CWelsh people awarded the King's
OL,4,Cbirthday honours
OL,6,FOther community champions celebrated
OL,7,Finclude:
OL,9,FSudha Bhatt: Honoured for her crucial
OL,10,Fservices to Community Cohesion in
OL,11,FCardiff, bridging cultural gaps and
OL,12,Ffostering inclusivity.
OL,14,FAndrew Charles Bowden: Awarded for his
OL,15,Fdedicated services to Housing and
OL,16,Flocal community development in Mould,
OL,17,FClwyd.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/8
